comments: Powell's (DAL) hands come forward slightly and marginal contact occurs with Paul's (PHX) front as Paul goes under the pick.

Paul (PHX) brings his left arm toward Doncic's (DAL) path and marginal contact occurs with Doncic's front as Doncic drives into the lane. Paul then brushes Doncic's right forearm and marginal contact occurs prior to Doncic's gather.
Doncic (DAL) raises his arm up to pursue the rebound and marginal contact occurs with Paul's (PHX) right arm as Paul secures the ball.
Doncic (DAL) forcefully knocks Paul's (PHX) legal hand off his side.
Paul (PHX) maintains a rested left forearm on Doncic's (DAL) side and then brushes Doncic's right leg in the post.
Wainright (PHX) moves forward into Doncic (DAL) and initiates arm/body contact during Doncic's upward shooting motion.
Ayton (PHX) establishes himself in Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Powell (DAL) clamps and holds Ayton's (PHX) left arm, affecting Ayton's ability to pursue the rebound.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) is moving alongside Booker's (PHX) path when marginal body contact occurs after Booker's gather.
Irving (DAL) grasps and then quickly releases Ayton's (PHX) right arm during the rebound.
Irving (DAL) brings his left arm toward Ayton's (PHX) front and marginal contact occurs during Ayton's put-back attempt.
Ayton (PHX) makes contact with the ball after it exits the imaginary cylinder above the rim.
Paul (PHX) maintains a rested forearm on Doncic's (DAL) front as he drives inside the perimeter.
Ayton (PHX) brings his left arm outward slightly and marginal contact occurs with Powell's (DAL) front as Powell completes the alley-oop attempt.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) maintains a legal guarding position on Durant's (PHX) drive
Bullock (DAL) brushes Durant's (PHX) left arm and marginal contact occurs during Durant's upward shooting motion. Hardaway Jr. (DAL) legally contests Durant's jump shot attempt.
Okogie (PHX) engages and disengages with Doncic (DAL) during the inbound.
Doncic (DAL) goes to, not through, Okogie's (PHX) space, as they come together at the end of Doncic's drive.
Durant (PHX) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Durant (PHX) and Okogie (PHX) avoid making contact with Doncic (DAL) during Doncic's upward shooting motion.
Doncic (DAL) raises his arm up to pursue the rebound and marginal contact occurs with Durant's (PHX) right arm as Durant secures the ball.
Doncic (DAL) commits a take foul on Durant (PHX).
All Technical Fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
All Technical Fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
After communicating with the Replay Center, it was determined that Dallas had the correct number of players on the court during the free throw attempt.
Durant (PHX) legally contests Doncic's (DAL) jump shot attempt.
Okogie (PHX) makes clean contact with the ball and bats it backward prior to incidental arm contact occurring.
